name: dialpad-logo
desc: Dialpad logo in full color. Wordmark responds to theme.

desc: Dialpad logo in full color with inverted wordmark. Wordmark responds to theme's primary inverted foreground color.

desc: Dialpad logo with wordmark in black, irrespective of theme.

name: dialpad-logo-white
desc: Dialpad logo with wordmark in white, irrespective of theme.

name: dialpad-mono-black
desc: Dialpad logo in black monochrome, irrespective of theme.

name: dialpad-mono-white
desc: Dialpad logo in white monochrome, irrespective of theme.

name: dialpad-wordmark
desc: Dialpad wordmark only. Color responds to theme's primary foreground color.

name: dialpad-wordmark-inverted
desc: Dialpad wordmark only. Color responds to theme's primary inverted foreground color.

name: dialpad-wordmark-black
desc: Dialpad wordmark only in black, irrespective of theme.

name: dialpad-wordmark-white
desc: Dialpad wordmark only in white, irrespective of theme.
